<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>There is mistake for polish plural rule.</p>

<p>The rule is:
return ($number == 1) ? 0 : ((($number % 10 &gt;= 2) &amp;&amp; ($number % 10 &lt;= 4) &amp;&amp; (($number % 100 &lt; 10) || ($number % 100 &gt; 29))) ? 1 : 2);
But should be:
return ($number == 1) ? 0 : ((($number % 10 &gt;= 2) &amp;&amp; ($number % 10 &lt;= 4) &amp;&amp; (($number % 100 &lt; 10) || ($number % 100 &gt; 19))) ? 1 : 2);</p>

<p>Patch will be attached.</p>

